# File format (according to p0f.fp) :
#
# wwww:ttt:D:ss:OOO...:QQ:OS:Details
#
# wwww    - window size
# ttt     - initial TTL
# D       - don't fragment bit  (0=unset, 1=set)
# ss      - overall SYN packet size
# OOO     - option value and order specification
# QQ      - quirks list
